<number id="3DFC24ADBC376E0F6DF4768DBCF52AF7" box="[969,1004,1923,1947]" pageId="7" pageNumber="384" value="2.7">2.7</number>
times longer than wide. Antennae 
<number id="3DFC24ADBC376E0F6BBD768DBA852AF7" box="[1408,1436,1923,1947]" pageId="7" pageNumber="384" value="19.0">19</number>
